title: Dell PowerVault ME5: System Health
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Reports the overall health of a Dell PowerVault ME5 storage system together
 with management-controller redundancy: the redundancy status, the operational
 status of each controller and the status of the partner management controller.

 State is taken from the system health value reported by the array. The mapping
 of the degraded, fault, unknown, not-redundant, controller-down and partner
 management controller conditions is configurable via the "Dell PowerVault ME5
 system health" ruleset.

discovery:
 One service is created per array.
